metadata.name: Liquit Color #1
metadata.description:
Collection 1/1 of illustrations and animations of pouring art, also known as fluid art or flow art.

Maked by Alex Jes√∫s Cabello Leiva - AlexCocoPro. 

The content of this gallery of abstract art related to action painting, aims to be like surrealized automatic writing taken to the field of illustration and animation, obtaining a certain psychedelic character, free, pure, with an autonomous visual language, with its own meaning, reflecting more intimate emotions and feelings.
